summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the City Engineer to incur an indebtedness against the General Fund of The City of Seattle, in the sum of Three Hundred Twenty-eight and 15/100 Dollars ($328.15), for the purpose of completing the improvement of Lakedell Avenue et al., by planking the same, as authorized by Ordinance No. 22110, creating Local Improvement District No. 2198.
